trailingComments.value:
* * Sets how the nodes are organized within this tree view. * * Accepted values are: * * * "containment" - organizes the nodes to indicate the containment hierarchy of the IFC objects. * * "types" - groups the nodes within their IFC types. * * "storeys" - groups the nodes within ````IfcBuildingStoreys```` and sub-groups them by their IFC types. * *
* This can be updated dynamically. * * Default value is "containment". * * @type {String}
